| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3557 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9cf5b2af-650c-5ddd-8ad7-942e93a401e0"
